    "The aim is not to provide a complete list of all projects, but to provide an overview and look in particular at advanced digital twins in ports.",
    "In the following, an outline of practical projects is given, sorted by the digital twin implementation level.",
    "This is combined and put into perspective regarding the existing literature.",
    "About one third of the literature contains a use case showcasing the functions of the digital twin studied.",
    "It varies whether these use cases refer to a real use case, if several use cases are analyzed or if a fictional use case is considered."
